  <div class="lesson-content-memo"> Mass or energy </div>   

  The speed of light is a constant, 
  so one way to regard E=mc<sup>2</sup> is as a conversion between units of mass and energy.
  Mass is a form of energy, so 
  in energy conservation calculations, the rest mass energy has to be included.
